Do not publish as a model artifact unless:

```text
[ ] License check passed
[ ] Payload integrity check passed
[ ] Qualitative before/after examples prepared
[ ] At least one task-specific evaluation completed
[ ] Failure cases documented
[ ] Runtime route application verified
[ ] Rollback/checksum validation passed
[ ] Model card includes limitations
```

If any of the following fail, publish only a report:

```text
[ ] redistribution license unclear
[ ] task output unstable
[ ] projected route causes severe repetition
[ ] route fails checksum rollback
[ ] route cannot be reproduced
```

