## 18. Main Risk Register

| Risk                                    | Severity | Mitigation                                                  |
| --------------------------------------- | -------: | ----------------------------------------------------------- |
| Task score below base                   |     High | Publish as negative/stress result or do not publish weights |
| License ambiguity                       | Critical | Publish report only                                         |
| Repetition / instability                |     High | Add failure cases; mark as unsafe                           |
| Overclaiming 7B/14B transfer            | Critical | Use “adapter behavior projection” wording                   |
| No visible before/after                 |     High | Do not launch publicly                                      |
| Source adapter incompatible             |   Medium | Try Qwen-family source first                                |
| HF artifact ignored                     |   Medium | Use strong model card + examples + social launch            |
| Evaluation too weak                     |     High | Include at least syntax validity + judge preference         |
| Runtime works but task does not improve |   Medium | Frame as behavior survival / diagnostic result              |

