## 19. Final Public Positioning

Recommended:

```text
Qwen2.5-0.5B SQL Adapter Projection is a no-retraining adapter-behavior survival experiment.
```

Avoid:

```text
We compressed a 14B SQL model into 0.5B.
```

Best balanced claim:

```text
This release tests whether task behavior from a larger SQL/Coding adapter can survive projection into Qwen2.5-0.5B. The target runtime uses only the 0.5B model and the projected adapter payload. Results include before/after examples, task metrics, runtime rollback validation, and failure cases.
```

